data.description: This adorable Windsor Park home is only a few minutes away from the Mathis Bridge that takes you into the shore communities of Seaside Heights, Seaside Park, Island Beach State Park, Lavallette and Ortley Beaches.  In this waterfront, sought out community of Windsor Park, this well-kept home is right off Rt 37 making easy access to all the main roads in and around Toms River. Looking to downsize or maybe just starting off, this home is a must see!
